title: John Bolton on Obama’s Legacy: America ‘Endangered Now on Fronts That Were Inconceivable Eight Years Ago’
text: WASHINGTON, DC - DECEMBER 13: U.S. President Barack Obama delivers remarks before signing the 21st Century Cures Act into law at the Eisenhower Executive Office Building December 13, 2016 in Washington, DC. The legislation eases the development and approval of experimental treatments and reforms federal policy on mental health care. (Photo by Chip Somodevilla/Getty Images)
